---
title: Maple Pecan Pie Squares Serves 4 | with Chocolate Chips and Shortbread Crust
description: These easy pecan pie bars are your solution to Thanksgiving dessert, without all the hassle! Bursting with buttery pecans and a hint of maple syrup, these gooey squares will have you reaching for seconds and thirds in no time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/maple-pecan-pie-squares-0ef64a0b-142d8570.jpg
